<lb/><p>Sirs,</p>
<lb/><p>My Father advises 
<lb/>me to write &amp; say 
<lb/>he is much obliged 
<lb/>to you for the footnotes, 
<lb/>&amp; if he is in Oxford 
<lb/>will be most happy 
<lb/>to sit for his portrait 
<lb/>He hopes you will 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002645_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<lb/>excuse his not writing 
<lb/>to you himself, but 
<lb/>his time is so much 
<lb/>occupied.</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">Yours truly</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">Agnes Livingstone</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">For</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">D<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Livingstone</p>
			
